skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: guess the month
des: Guess the Month is a quiz to provide the correct month for a particular event. Launch the skill by the name and answer questions by saying a number between 1 and 4. If you don't know the answer, you can skip. To hear again you can ask to repeat.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
